                                                                <p><img class="inset-right" src="assets/img/wojooh.jpg" alt=""></p>
                                                                <p>Wojooh, formally known as “Faces”, is a beauty haven filled to the brim with a tantalising array of fragrance, make-up and skincare products. Thanks to its innate understanding of the Middle East women’s beauty desires and concerns, Wojooh offers a sophisticated fusion of luxury, unconventional niche and specialty brands as well as expert advice to fulfil every need of the beauty savvy. In 2014, Wojooh launched ‘Wow by Wojooh’, the first make-up line inspired by the Middle East consumer.</p>
